        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " function is a scalar function in Microsoft SQL Server designed to generate a new tracking number for invoices. Scalar functions return a single value, which in this case is the newly generated invoice tracking number. This function is used in scenarios where unique identifiers are required for tracking invoices within a database system."
